<paragraph pageId="676" pageNumber="677">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Casey" authorityYear="1884" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Amerinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="676" pageNumber="677" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Amerinus</taxonomicName>
Casey, 1884b: 7. Type species: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="LeConte" authorityYear="1863" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Bradycellus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="676" pageNumber="677" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="linearis">
